===小學及初中===
[[小學|小學]]學生(12歲或以下人士)一般在[[法律|法律]]上未達[[最低合法性交年齡|最低合法性交年齡]]，當師生戀發生在小學校園內，常因違反教師任用相關法令或是與未成年學生發生[[性行為|性行為]]而產生[[性侵害|性侵害]]刑責<ref>{{Cite web|title=國小師生不倫戀 分手鬧成性虐|url=https://tw.news.yahoo.com/國小師生不倫戀-分手鬧成性虐-213000566.html|access-date=2022-02-12|work=tw.news.yahoo.com|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2022-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220212154230/https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8F%E5%B8%AB%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%8D%E5%80%AB%E6%88%80-%E5%88%86%E6%89%8B%E9%AC%A7%E6%88%90%E6%80%A7%E8%99%90-213000566.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[http://news.hotpot.hk/fruit/art_main.php?iss_id=20101201&sec_id=4104&art_id=14719253 男教師涉濕吻胸襲小六女生 師生畸戀控非禮]{{dead link|date=2018年2月|bot=InternetArchiveBot|fix-attempted=yes}}</ref>。

同樣地，由於[[國中|國中]]生(15歲或以下人士)在[[中華民國法律|中華民國法律]]一般都未到可[[最低合法性行為年齡|合法地進行性行為的年齡]]，因此當師生戀發生在初中校園內，常因違反教師任用相關法令或是與未成年學生發生[[性行為|性行為]]而產生[[性侵害|性侵害]]刑責<ref>{{Cite web|title=产业问诊室 地契号码不同 买错房子住错屋？|url=https://www.sinchew.com.my/20071017/%e4%ba%a7%e4%b8%9a%e9%97%ae%e8%af%8a%e5%ae%a4%e5%9c%b0%e5%a5%91%e5%8f%b7%e7%a0%81%e4%b8%8d%e5%90%8c%e4%b9%b0%e9%94%99%e6%88%bf%e5%ad%90%e4%bd%8f%e9%94%99%e5%b1%8b%ef%bc%9f/|access-date=2022-02-12|date=2007-10-17|work=星洲网 Sin Chew Daily|language=en|archive-date=2022-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220212103751/https://www.sinchew.com.my/20071017/%E4%BA%A7%E4%B8%9A%E9%97%AE%E8%AF%8A%E5%AE%A4%E5%9C%B0%E5%A5%91%E5%8F%B7%E7%A0%81%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E4%B9%B0%E9%94%99%E6%88%BF%E5%AD%90%E4%BD%8F%E9%94%99%E5%B1%8B%EF%BC%9F/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/local/20120723/133790 |title=與國中女嘿咻　音樂老師判6年定讞 |access-date=2012-07-23 |archive-date=2012-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120828005433/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/local/20120723/133790 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://tw.nextmedia.com/rnews/article/SecID/102/art_id/83291/IssueID/20111019 抓奶狼成淫師　誘戀國中女性交]{{Dead link|date=2020年1月|bot=InternetArchiveBot|fix-attempted=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://web.pts.org.tw/php/news/pts_news/detail.php?NEENO=194792 |title=教部明令禁止師生戀 違者可予解聘 |access-date=2011-10-31 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304131321/http://web.pts.org.tw/php/news/pts_news/detail.php?NEENO=194792 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=性侵犯混進國中 淫師劈腿2少女 迫塞跳蛋|url=http://tw.nextmedia.com/applenews/article/art_id/33910612/IssueID/20111224|access-date=2011-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111224062043/http://tw.nextmedia.com/applenews/article/art_id/33910612/IssueID/20111224|archive-date=2011-12-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=男師嘿咻國二女 「我床都是妳香味」|url=https://tw.appledaily.com/headline/20120807/N3JZ3YWF4DSSN7PHABPGRNLZOM/|